## 🔬 Technical Specifications Summary

| Parameter | Value | Notes |
|-----------|-------|-------|
| Baud Rate | 250 | Down from 500 for reliability |
| Sample Rate | 44.1 kHz | Standard audio CD quality |
| Mark Frequency | 1200 Hz | Binary 1 |
| Space Frequency | 2200 Hz | Binary 0 |
| Modulation | AFSK | Audio Frequency Shift Keying |
| Demodulation | Zero-Crossing | Counts samples between sign changes |
| Protocol | Custom | Sync + Length + Type + Payload + Checksum |
| Encryption | XOR | Basic obfuscation only |
| Max Payload | 255 bytes | Limited by 1-byte length field |
| File Chunk Size | 200 bytes | Balances packet loss vs overhead |
| Preamble | 1200 ms | For VOX triggering |
| Squelch Threshold | 0.01 RMS | 1% of maximum signal |

