## 🎯 Quick Reference

**To Send Text**: Type message → Click "Send text"  
**To Send File**: Click "Send file" → Select file → Confirm  
**To Receive**: Just listen - automatic  
**To View Files**: Click "Open Received Files" button  
**To Change Key**: Edit "Encryption Key" field (auto-saves)  
**To Test**: Run in Debug mode - tests run automatically  

**Default Settings**:
- Encryption Key: "RADIO"
- Baud Rate: 250
- Input Gain: 1.0x
- Compress Images: ON

**Status Indicators**:
- Input/Output Frequency: Should show 1000-2500 Hz during transmission
- Input/Output Volume: Should show bars during audio activity
- System Log: Shows all transmitted/received data
- Transfer Progress: File transfer percentage
